&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot; data-sourcepos=&quot;16:1-16:352;2182-2533&quot;&gt;Build and support integrations with existing mission systems. Connect UDS Data Capability to legacy databases, flat-file drops, SOAP/REST endpoints, message buses, existing object storage, and identity providers (Keycloak, mission-side SSO). Prior experience integrating with these types of systems is more relevant than experience building on them.&lt;/li&gt;
